      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS system. This example delivers linear power delivery and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and updated bushings, while the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement through every gate. Maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing service and a valve adjustment. The factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal power distribution out of apexes. Finished in Carbon Black, the paint retains a deep luster despite minor road wear consistent with enthusiast use.",
